<P><H1 align=center>BANK / CREDIT CARD DETAILS – DC080</H1>
<P align=center></P>
<P><FONT color=red><STRONG>NOTE: </STRONG>areas shown in 
red are mandatory and must be completed to proceed</FONT>            </P>
<P>This screen collects details of any bank or credit cards held by the 
applicant. This is important in assessing the applicant’s suitability, and 
affordability, and is part of the overall credit assessment If the applicant has 
any bank or credit cards, click the ‘Yes’ radio button at the top of the screen. 
This will enable the ‘Add’ button</P>
<P><H3>Add: </H3>clicking on the ‘Add’ button leads to <A HREF="HELP_DC081.asp">Add / 
Edit Bank / Credit Cards (DC081)</A>. Any details entered on this screen will be 
summarised in DC080.
<P></P>
